[TYPE: docker exec nmea-gnss-driver-cats-testing cats -s config/gpsfake_nmea.xml -pr gherkin -t tests/gherkin_group/gpsfake_nmea/gpsfake_nmea_test.feature]

And there it is — two scenarios, both passing. The first one sends an NMEA sentence over TCP, the second one over UDP. Both validate the echo matches.

